  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large pot over medium heat. Add beef and brown on all sides.",
    "Add onions and garlic, cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, cooking for an additional minute.",
    "Pour in crushed tomatoes, red wine, oregano, cinnamon, bay leaf, and broth. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 1 hour.",
    "Reduce heat to low, stir in cheese until melted. Stir in lemon juice.",
    "Simmer for an additional 30 minutes to let flavors meld together.",
    "Serve hot with crusty bread."
